      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Crush your <strong>garlic</strong> open by squashing it with the side of a knife and remove the skin</p><p>Add your <strong>tomato wedges</strong>, <strong>crushed garlic</strong> and <strong>butternut squash cubes </strong>to the dish</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1680107564967-x200.jpg",
